Adeliade Aronio is an artist based in East London. Her works often involve painting murals on the outside of buildings and structures and she is available for commissions.  

She also runs after-school art classes for children in her home studio in Bow. The sessions focus on art history, teaching practical skills and play. 

You can contact her on hello@adelaidearonio.com to discuss either.



